    "Id": "chassisdef_thunder_stallion_TST-DRG",
    "Name": "Thunder Stallion",
    "Details": "This Thunder Stallion was named after Dragoons, ancient Terran warriors that rode to battle on horseback to then dismount and fight on foot. Some History buff named this Mech, don't ask me where he learned all that history from though. This Thunder Stallion comes equipped with a Heavy PPC, one Heavy Gauss Rifle and two Clan LRM20's. While not as fast as its namesake, this thing will still provide ample support from the rear or flanks. It can be counted on to do this well, with Sniper Sensors for eyes and an Angel ECM for ears.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Distracting</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.27</color></b>",
